Package: dplyrpggeo
Type: Package
Title: Convenience functions for working with PostGIS geospatial data using dplyr.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-09-25
Author: Brad Dixon
Maintainer: Brad Dixon <rbdixon@gmail.com>
Depends: dplyr (>= 0.4.3), RPostgreSQL (>= 0.4), assertthat
SystemRequirements: PostgreSQL with PostGIS extensions
Description: This package extends dplyr's native PostgreSQL capabilities with functions for
 working with geospatial data stored using the PostGIS extensions to PostgreSQL.
License: MIT
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: knitr,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
